msgstr "Ny yllir esperthi an alhwedhow"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/import_export_keys_subpage.rs:354
msgid "The passphrase doesn't match the one used to export the keys."
msgstr ""
"An lavaren-tremena nag a omdhesedh an lavaren devndyhys rag esperthi an "
"alhwedhow."

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/import_export_keys_subpage.rs:359
msgid "Could not import the keys"
msgstr "Ny yllir ynperthi an alhwedhow"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.blp:6
msgid "Encryption"
msgstr "Argelesans"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.blp:10
msgid "Crypto Identity"
msgstr "Honanieth Grypto"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.blp:11
msgid ""
"Allows you to verify other Matrix accounts and automatically trust their "
"verified sessions"
msgstr ""
"Gallosegi dhywgh dhe wirhe akontys Matrix erel hag afydhya yn awtomatek aga "
"esedhegow wirhes"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.blp:75
msgid "Account Recovery"
msgstr "Daskavos Akont"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.blp:77
msgid ""
"Allows to fully recover your account with a recovery key or passphrase, if "
"you ever lose access to all your sessions"
msgstr ""
"Gasa dhe dhaskavos agas akont gans alhwedh daskavos po lavaren-tremena, mar "
"hwi a gell hedhas dhe oll a'gas esedhegow"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:151
msgid "No Crypto Identity"
msgstr "Honanieth Grypto Vyth"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:153
msgid "Verifying your own devices or other users is not possible"
msgstr "Ow kwirhe devisyow a'gas honan po devnydhoryon erel nag yw possybyl"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:156
#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:229
msgid "Enable…"
msgstr "Bywhe…"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:159
msgid "Enable Crypto Identity"
msgstr "Bywhe Honanieth Grypto"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:175
msgid "Crypto Identity Enabled"
msgstr "Honanieth Grypto Byw"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:177
msgid "The crypto identity exists and this device is verified"
msgstr "Yma an honanieth grypto hag an devis ma yw gwirhes"

#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:180
#: src/account_settings/encryption_page/mod.rs:248
msgid "Reset…"
msgstr "Dassettya…"

